      <acqinfo encodinganalog="541">
         <head>Provenance</head>
         <p> The papers of Samuel Hay Kauffmann, newspaperman, art historian, and
		  author, were given to the Library by Kauffmann's estate in 1931.</p>
      </acqinfo>
      <processinfo encodinganalog="583">
         <head>Processing History</head>
         <p>The papers of Samuel Hay Kauffman were arranged and described in 1983
		  and 1985. The finding aid was revised in 2010.</p>
      </processinfo>
      <userestrict encodinganalog="540">
